lead_paragraph: Given England coach Eddie Jones already considered Australia's media "disrespectful" during last June's test series, he would probably not have enjoyed his depiction as a "malevolent clown" in a national newspaper on Saturday.

headline.print_headline: Jones Dubbed 'Menacing Clown' in Australian Media
